  "description": "A close-up photograph captures a portion of a butterfly wing, showcasing intricate details and vibrant colors. The wing is predominantly black, with a mesmerizing iridescent sheen of blues, greens, and purples. Its edges are uniquely scalloped and bordered by a crisp white fringe, resembling delicate lace. The background is a soft, out-of-focus green, hinting at foliage and a natural environment. The wing's texture appears velvety and subtly patterned, drawing the viewer's eye to its complexity. This is a macro shot with extremely shallow depth of field.",
